{"tid":1689762,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"傳名創優品計劃明年上市 集資最多10億美元","createTime":"2019-11-03T03:53:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T04:02:54.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"34bf565903d1d69f6eaef9c8701078f3c6e4cbed","tid":1689762,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T03:53:57.000Z","msg":"路透旗下IFR報道，和日本無印良品走相似路線的名創優品﹙MINISO﹚計劃在明年上市，集資額為5億至10億美元。據報公司已聘請美國銀行及高盛安排上市，惟目前地點未定，選址包括香港或美國。<br />\n名創優品在2013年成立，在全球80個國家都有分店，數目約3,500家，去年銷售額為170億元人民幣，公司目標是在2022年的分店總數達10,000家。無印良品在2018年的分店數目為975家。<br />\n公司去年獲騰訊（700）及Hillhouse Capital等投資10億元人民幣，去年市值為22億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191102/60223189\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191102%2F60223189&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpBYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=636ba5be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191102%2F60223189&h=b9fb4084\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191102/60223189</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560276e36818ee17318d5cee2e640d2a54d6c011","tid":1689762,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T03:55:55.000Z","msg":"臉皮厚撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888746aaf1348d91e92157c175c7b926c7cb5aa9","tid":1689762,"uid":166947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T03:57:06.000Z","msg":"槍打出頭鳥"},{"pid":"41a4bdb39dd6465c69c8bf44333a64b98ffb0fba","tid":1689762,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":